						<div class="postbody">And the corrected Truth logic for MAD-R. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /><br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">&nbsp; &nbsp;OUT0 = ((!(!A2 &amp;&amp; !A3) &amp;&amp; !_ROM &amp;&amp; !MODE) || _ROM || (A2 &amp;&amp; !_ROM &amp;&amp; MODE &amp;&amp; _RESET) || !_RESET) &amp;&amp; (Vbat &lt; Vcc);<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;OUT1 = ((!(A2 &amp;&amp; !A3) &amp;&amp; !_ROM &amp;&amp; !MODE) || _ROM || (!A2 &amp;&amp; !_ROM &amp;&amp; MODE &amp;&amp; _RESET) || !_RESET) &amp;&amp; (Vbat &lt; Vcc);<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;OUT2 = ((!((A0 &amp;&amp; A1 &amp;&amp; A2 &amp;&amp; !A3 &amp;&amp; _ROM &amp;&amp; MODE &amp;&amp; _RESET) || (!A0 &amp;&amp; A1 &amp;&amp; A2 &amp;&amp; A3 &amp;&amp; !_ROM &amp;&amp; !MODE &amp;&amp; _RESET))) &amp;&amp; (Vbat &lt; Vcc)) || (Vbat &gt;= Vcc);<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;OUT3 = (!((!A2 &amp;&amp; A3 &amp;&amp; !_ROM &amp;&amp; !MODE) || (A0 &amp;&amp; A1 &amp;&amp; !A2 &amp;&amp; !A3 &amp;&amp; _ROM &amp;&amp; MODE &amp;&amp; _RESET)) || !_RESET) &amp;&amp; (Vbat &lt; Vcc);<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;OUT4 = (!_RESET) &amp;&amp; (Vbat &lt; Vcc);<br /></div></div>

